## Limitations

This report is based on available data and public opinion polls, which may not capture the full complexity of individual beliefs and regional differences. Additionally, the data is subject to change as new events and studies emerge. The reliance on secondary sources means that the findings are contingent on the accuracy and objectivity of the original data providers. Furthermore, the report does not delve into the counterarguments against gun control, which are also a significant part of the broader debate.